    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at this model risk level per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. CFD predictions of hemolysis index agree with experimental data within 15% across all operating conditions, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Experimental evidence from bench testing and published literature supports the overall credibility conclusion. The hemolysis prediction claim is considered supported by the weight of computational and experimental evidence reviewed during assessment.",
